The paper deals with game theory and mechanism design, which are central topics in cs.GT (Game Theory and Economics) and cs.MA (Multiagent Systems). The repeated sales setting involves decision-making over time, which is a common theme in cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.IT (Information Theory). Finally, the paper uses mathematical analysis to derive results, which is a common approach in cs.LG (Machine Learning).
